ong>22 min\/Varoma\/speed 3<\/strong>.","This easy recipe can be frozen for up to 6 months, just omit the peas. Cook then allow to cool before freezing. To re-heat, allow to defrost then reheat in oven, adding a little stock if needed, for 30-40 minutes until chicken is tender, adding frozen peas 5 minutes before serving."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","1h 30m","8 portions"]}